<br />
<br />Sorry for the slightly off-topic question, but why do so many people post their projects in a 7zip format? Why not use the more universal/common .zip? (Isn't it more common?) I haven't bothered to install some of these games because of that. I know it wouldn't be hard for me to install 7zip, but I'm lazy like that.

		

