		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Since I didn't have WinRar on my new laptop yet, and didn't know it supported this, I had to find a tool to do it. Three failed to work, and one finally did but I had to find the right app of the 3 it gave me. It compressed nicely, at only 2K, but it still isn't that big and was a HUGE hassle without having winrar on my system. ZIP is good enough and more common, I'd suggest using it, but do however you wish. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />

		

		</td>
